      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"your existence matters\" thing... it just feels like something people say to be nice. It doesn't change the reality. If I didn't show up to work or if I just stopped replying to texts, it would take weeks, maybe months, for anyone to even wonder where I went. It’s not like I’m a main character in anyone's life. I'm just... background noise.",
